    <div class="mission">
        <h1>our mission</h1>
        <p>
            Our Mission at the Discovery nursery is to develop the “Whole Child”, where the children gain confidence through the acquisition of basic skills. We establish in children love for learning, strong work ethics, creativity, respect .
        </p>
        <br>
        <video loop="loop" autoplay="autoplay" muted="muted">
            <source src="~/Content/Images/good.mp4">
