    </div>


    <div class="building-background container-fluid">
        <div>
            <br>
            <p class="answer">Why do you choose us ?!</p>
        </div>


        <div class="container">

            <div class="mt-5 row">
                <div class="building d-flex align-items-center h-100 col-md-6">
                    <p>
                        Education at Discovery nursery is like a beautiful dance where teachers, parents, and students collaborate in a loving and nurturing, academically rich environment. Each student’s unique strengths, weaknesses and gifts are embraced and supported as we celebrate new milestones, both big and small, together.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="d-flex align-items-center col-md-6">
                    <img style="z-index: 1; width: 100vw;height: 50vh;" class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/Images/ga.jpg">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5 row">

                <div class="d-flex align-items-center col-md-6">
                    <img style="z-index: 1; width: 100vw;height: 50vh;" class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/Images/22.jpg">
                </div>

                <div class="building d-flex align-items-center h-100 col-md-6">
                    <p>
                        With proper care and education, every child can reach his or her full potential.
                        The more parents understand about how a child grows, the better prepared they’ll be to recognize special needs – and seek help promptly.
                        Children with special needs require extra attention, teaching, care and love!
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>



            <div class="mt-5 row">
                <div class="building d-flex align-items-center h-100 col-md-6">
                    <p>
                        Teachers work to promote and manage the growth of their students in conjunction with their special needs.
                        Our Teachers will modify the general education curriculum to make sure each student’s special individual needs are met.
                        They patient, accepting, understanding and they know how to discovery each child's talent.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="d-flex align-items-center col-md-6">
                    <img style="z-index: 1; width: 100vw;height: 50vh;" class="img-fluid" src="~/Content/Images/kk.jpg">
                </div>
            </div>


        </div>
    </div>


